#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
O-Health Kiosk vitals capture — patient state machine with 19-LED indicator.

LED layout (19 LEDs total):
  LEDs 0, 1, 2, 3 -> BP machine      (breathing green during step 1 + after lockout)
  LEDs 4, 5       -> Mic              (on the full 3-minute post-flow window)
  LEDs 6, 7       -> SpO2 sensor      (breathing green during step 2)
  LED  8          -> Glucometer       (placeholder; on for 10s at start of post-flow)
  LEDs 9..12      -> Kiosk Logo       (Always On - Solid White)
  LEDs 13..18     -> Camera System    (Always On - Solid White)

Per-patient flow:
  STEP 1 — wait for BP cuff power-on + capture.       BP LEDs breathing green.
  STEP 2 — wait for finger insertion + SpO2 capture.   SpO2 LEDs breathing green.
  STEP 3 — temp read (BLE TR-FR400 / I2C) + push.      All LEDs off briefly.
  HARD 3-MIN LOCKOUT — post-flow LEDs run.              BP detection ignored.

Run as root for LED hardware access:
  sudo python3 sensor_all.py
"""
